{"_id":"GxwAJ9Q0zWFc3qDL","name":"Resupply","permission":{"default":0,"80dTBjQxhMnkxgsJ":3},"type":"move","data":{"category":"quest","description":"<p>When <strong>you hunt, forage, or scavenge</strong>, ((rollplus wits)).</p>\n<p>On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, you bolster your resources. Take +2 supply.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>weak hit</strong>, take up to +2 supply, but suffer -1 momentum for each.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>miss</strong>, you find nothing helpful. <em>Pay the Price</em>.</p>"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.r4uFec2zkDRnWK1p"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"WVCKAwfTadxE4Vs1","name":"Enter the Fray","permission":{"default":0,"80dTBjQxhMnkxgsJ":3},"type":"move","data":{"category":"combat","description":"<p>When <strong>you enter into combat</strong>, set the rank of each of your foes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Troublesome foe: 3 progress per harm; inflicts 1 harm.</li>\n<li>Dangerous foe: 2 progress per harm; inflicts 2 harm.</li>\n<li>Formidable foe: 1 progress per harm; inflicts 3 harm.</li>\n<li>Extreme foe: 2 ticks per harm; inflicts 4 harm.</li>\n<li>Epic foe: 1 tick per harm; inflicts 5 harm.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Then, roll to determine who is in control. If you are...</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Facing off against your foe: @ironsworn.moveRoll[attr:heart].</li>\n<li>Moving into position against an unaware foe, or striking without warning: ((rollplus shadow)).</li>\n<li>Ambushed: ((rollplus wits)).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, take +2 momentum. You have initiative.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>weak hit</strong>, choose one.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bolster your position: Take +2 momentum.</li>\n<li>Take initiative.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On a <strong>miss</strong>, combat begins with you at a disadvantage. <em>Pay the Price</em>. Your foe has initiative.</p>"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.j9JQRHdUkMHHkmIZ"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"dbqrGyQ6siXtcdkO","name":"Heal","permission":{"default":0,"80dTBjQxhMnkxgsJ":3},"type":"move","data":{"category":"suffer","description":"<p>When <strong>you treat an injury or ailment</strong>, ((rollplus wits)). If you are mending your own wounds, ((rollplus wits)) or ((rollpllus iron)), whichever is lower.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, your care is helpful. If you (or the ally under your care) have the wounded condition, you may clear it. Then, take or give up to +2 health.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>weak hit</strong>, as above, but you must suffer -1 supply or -1 momentum (your choice).</p>\n<p>On a <strong>miss</strong>, your your aid is ineffective. <em>Pay the Price</em>.</p>"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ZUxHNnIba3Pws6sg"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"fUrUUBjbNT8KW2TV","name":"Battle","permission":{"default":0,"80dTBjQxhMnkxgsJ":3},"type":"move","data":{"category":"adventure","description":"<p>When <strong>you fight a battle, and it happens in a blur</strong>, envision your objective and roll. If you primarily...</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fight at range, or using your speed and the terrain to your advantage: ((rollplus edge)).</li>\n<li>Fight depending on your courage, allies, or companions: ((rollplus heart)).</li>\n<li>Fight in close to overpower your opponents: ((rollplus iron)).</li>\n<li>Fight using trickery to befuddle your opponents: ((rollplus shadow)).</li>\n<li>Fight using careful tactics to outsmart your opponents: ((rollplus wits)).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, you achieve your objective unconditionally. Take +2 momentum.</p>\n<p>On a <strong>weak hit</strong>, you achieve your objective, but not without cost. <em>Pay the Price.</em></p>\n<p>On a <strong>miss</strong>, you are defeated and the objective is lost to you. <em>Pay the Price.</em></p>"},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wM1GWPBUZTiDMshz"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
